    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Iustitia pariter ac <lb n="2"/>pietate caelestibus <expan><abbr>adq</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Romanae felicitatis perpe<lb break="no" n="4"/>tuis fundatoribus <expan><abbr>d<am>d</am></abbr><ex>ominis</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>ostris</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Valentiniano et Valenti <lb n="6"/>victoriosissimis principi<lb break="no" n="7"/>bus ac totius orbis <expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustis</ex></expan> <lb n="8"/>Antonius Dracontius <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ir</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimus</ex></expan> <lb n="9"/><expan><abbr>ag</abbr><ex>ens</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>vic</abbr><ex>es</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ectorum</ex></expan> praetorio per <lb n="10"/>Africanas provincias ni<lb break="no" n="11"/>mini <note>sic</note> et maiestati eorum <lb n="12"/>semper dicatissimus
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>The inscription is carved over two erased earlier texts. (B): Z. 7: AE 1929: aug; Z. 10-11: Bartoccini, AE 1929: nu/mini.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography">
                <listBibl><bibl>AE 1929, 0005. (B)</bibl><bibl>IRT 472.</bibl><bibl>R. Bartoccini, AI 2, 1928/29, 30-49. - AE 1929. (B)</bibl><bibl>PLRE 1 Dracontius 3.</bibl><bibl>I. Tantillo - F. Bigi (Hrsg.), Leptis Magna. Una città e le sue iscrizioni in epoca tardoromana (Cassino 2010) 242; 329-331, Nr. 9; fig. 10.11; tav. 25 (Zeichnung).</bibl><bibl/></listBibl>
            </div>
        </body>
